#: src/vajo_gui.py:1970
msgid ""
"Desktop: {}\n"
"\n"
"Your system is currently pinned to a rolled-back snapshot.\n"
"Updates and rollbacks are disabled while pinned.\n"
"\n"
"Click 'Unpin' to remove the pin. You can then roll back\n"
"further or do a full upgrade when ready."
msgstr ""
"桌面：{}\n"
"\n"
"您的系统当前已固定到回滚的快照。\n"
"固定期间，更新和回滚功能已禁用。\n"
"\n"
"点击“取消固定”以移除固定。之后您可以进一步回滚，\n"
"或在准备就绪后执行完整升级。"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:1977
msgid "Unpin"
msgstr "取消固定"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:1986 src/vajo_tui.py:577
msgid "Unpinning..."
msgstr "正在取消固定..."

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2006
msgid "Unpinned. You can now roll back further or upgrade."
msgstr "已取消固定。您现在可以进一步回滚或升级。"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2008 src/vajo_tui.py:591
msgid "Error during unpin"
msgstr "取消固定时出错"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2018 src/vajo_tui.py:1250
msgid "Checking rollback availability..."
msgstr "正在检查回滚可用性..."

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2023 src/vajo_tui.py:1259
msgid "Cannot determine current desktop version."
msgstr "无法确定当前桌面版本。"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2051 src/vajo_tui.py:1268
msgid "No previous version available to roll back to."
msgstr "没有可回滚的先前版本。"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2063 src/vajo_tui.py:1222
msgid "Select rollback target"
msgstr "选择回滚目标"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2069
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#: src/vajo_gui.py:2083
msgid ""
"<b>Choose a version to roll back to:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Rolling back will downgrade all system packages to the selected snapshot and "
"<b>lock the system to that point in time</b>. While pinned:\n"
"  • Repository syncs and upgrades are disabled\n"
"  • Package installs still work against the pinned snapshot\n"
"\n"
"You can unpin later via the same menu to resume normal updates."
msgstr ""
"<b>选择要回滚到的版本：</b>\n"
"\n"
"回滚会将所有系统软件包降级到所选快照，并<b>将系统锁定到该时间点</b>。固定期"
"间：\n"
"  • 仓库同步和升级已禁用\n"
"  • 软件包安装仍针对固定的快照进行\n"
"\n"
"您之后可以通过同一菜单取消固定以恢复正常更新。"

